@startuml sequence_product_search
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 200

title Product Search & Filter Flow [L2-001, L2-076]

actor Shopper
participant "ShopPage\n(app/(storefront)/shop/page.tsx)" as ShopPage
participant "ProductGrid\n(lib/features/product-grid.tsx)" as Grid
participant "Products API\n(app/api/catalog/products/route.ts)" as API
participant "Drizzle ORM\n(lib/db/schema/catalog.ts)" as ORM
database "PostgreSQL\ncatalog.products" as DB

== Initial Page Load ==

Shopper -> ShopPage : GET /shop?category=Bundle&texture=straight\n&sortBy=price&sortDirection=asc&page=1
activate ShopPage

ShopPage -> API : GET /api/catalog/products\n?category=Bundle&texture=straight\n&sortBy=price&sortDirection=asc\n&page=1&pageSize=12
activate API

API -> API : Parse searchParams:\ncategory, texture, sortBy,\nsortDirection, page, pageSize

API -> ORM : db.select().from(products)\n.where(and(\n  eq(products.type, "Bundle"),\n  eq(products.texture, "straight")\n))\n.orderBy(asc(products.price))\n.limit(12).offset(0)
activate ORM

ORM -> DB : SELECT * FROM catalog.products\nWHERE type = $1 AND texture = $2\nORDER BY price ASC\nLIMIT 12 OFFSET 0
activate DB
DB --> ORM : ResultSet (rows + count)
deactivate DB

ORM --> API : Product[]
deactivate ORM

API --> ShopPage : 200 OK\n{ items: Product[],\n  totalCount: 47,\n  page: 1, pageSize: 12 }
deactivate API

ShopPage -> Grid : <products={items}>
Grid --> Shopper : Rendered product grid\nwith pagination controls
deactivate ShopPage

== Pagination ==

Shopper -> ShopPage : Click "Page 2"
activate ShopPage
ShopPage -> API : GET /api/catalog/products\n?category=Bundle&texture=straight\n&sortBy=price&sortDirection=asc\n&page=2&pageSize=12
activate API
API -> ORM : .limit(12).offset(12)
activate ORM
ORM -> DB : SELECT ... LIMIT 12 OFFSET 12
activate DB
DB --> ORM : ResultSet
deactivate DB
ORM --> API : Product[]
deactivate ORM
API --> ShopPage : 200 OK { items, totalCount, page: 2, pageSize: 12 }
deactivate API
ShopPage -> Grid : <products={items}>
Grid --> Shopper : Page 2 results
deactivate ShopPage

@enduml
